308
00:36:43,260 --> 00:36:45,619
Da Fu and Chuan Yu are having a snowball fight.

309
00:36:45,619 --> 00:36:48,760
Come and eat. Cold food hurts your stomach.

310
00:37:13,700 --> 00:37:15,400
It's so good.

311
00:37:23,239 --> 00:37:25,119
What's this?

312
00:37:25,119 --> 00:37:27,419
Today is the Shunxing Festival.

313
00:37:30,660 --> 00:37:35,619
I planned to go to Kaiyuan Temple today to light a candle for my mother.

314
00:37:35,619 --> 00:37:37,919
But I was so busy that I forgot.

315
00:37:39,219 --> 00:37:43,660
Your fake husband went for you and even filled up the fragrant oil.

316
00:37:43,660 --> 00:37:47,619
These flower lanterns were brought from the temple.

317
00:37:47,619 --> 00:37:50,220
According to custom, nine lanterns should be lit in succession.

318
00:37:50,220 --> 00:37:54,999
This way, the immortals will bless your new year with happiness and success.

319
00:38:01,260 --> 00:38:02,760
Here.

320
00:38:17,660 --> 00:38:20,280
We're grasshoppers tied to the same rope.

321
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:24,220
If you have bad luck, I naturally won't fare well either.

322
00:38:24,220 --> 00:38:28,579
So, half of these blessing lanterns should go to you.

323
00:38:44,860 --> 00:38:49,419
Jiang Chang Yang, you brought me a midnight snack.

324
00:38:49,419 --> 00:38:53,900
You visited my mother and even helped me light the candles.

325
00:38:54,919 --> 00:39:00,280
You've done so much for me.

326
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:13,760
You said it yourself. We're allies.

327
00:39:14,300 --> 00:39:16,780
You're busy here because of His Majesty.

328
00:39:16,780 --> 00:39:21,519
I'm not good at growing flowers, but I can handle other things, right?

329
00:39:27,619 --> 00:39:30,580
The promised time is approaching.

330
00:39:30,580 --> 00:39:34,760
Will these peonies really bloom on time?

331
00:39:36,139 --> 00:39:37,939
Of course.

332
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:42,039
They can't speak. How do you know?

333
00:39:42,039 --> 00:39:46,820
I can predict their blooming time by feeling the softness of the buds.

334
00:39:46,820 --> 00:39:48,720
Really?

335
00:39:49,419 --> 00:39:50,700
Look.

336
00:39:50,700 --> 00:39:57,760
If this bud is as hard as your knuckles, then it'll take another month.

337
00:39:57,760 --> 00:40:02,539
When it gets as soft as your fingertips, there's about five days left.

338
00:40:05,419 --> 00:40:07,560
When it gets as soft as the side of your palm…

339
00:40:14,979 --> 00:40:16,779
Jiang Chang Yang.

340
00:40:19,180 --> 00:40:21,319
Why are your cheeks so red?

341
00:40:24,059 --> 00:40:27,600
The greenhouse is too hot. I'm going out for some air.

342
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:29,400
Wait a moment.

343
00:40:38,180 --> 00:40:42,800
It's cold outside. Put something on.

344
00:40:44,199 --> 00:40:46,300
Be careful not to catch a cold.

